message.body: I love you. It's awesome to have so many wonderful women in my life. I'm having donuts and doing yoga with the reiki school director in two weeks and I just can't get enough if the many awesome women in my life. xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
You too, wonderful strong lady. All about ladies. Love yourself more!xxxxxxxxxx
Hey fauble, I'm TIRED, I think I'm choosing sleep over morgan...have fun if you go xxxxx

Finch you lovely lovely girl, I needed sleep too! It was like I was wedded to my bed. I missed class but I like that we missed together. Plus in May, we can both start going to Thursday morning when my schedule changes.
